==English==
[[Image:Map of USA highlighting Nevada.png|thumb|right|Map of US highlighting Nevada]]

===Proper noun===
'''Nevada'''

#A {{USstate}} Capital: [[Carson City]].

===Pronunciation===
<!--  I don't know the correct linguistic symbols for this.  It'd be nice if someone put those in! -->
While outsiders typicaly pronounce the word "ne-vah-da", residents of Nevada actually pronounce the middle syllable as a short ''a'', as in the word [[cat]] or [[hat]].  (Residents often regard the pronunciation as a test of whether visitors, such as presidential candidates, have informed themselves about the state.)

